race.comment: OAK PARK MADDISON (12) couldn't meet her short quote when racing keenly through the middle stages at Strathalbyn last start. Strips fitter third-up and looks ready to repay the faith. SYNTHESISE (13) also didn't meet market expectations fresh but will have tightened up from that run and is suited stepping out over this longer journey. Crowther sticking is a strong push. REAL WORLD (4) exceeded expectations on debut at Murray Bridge, sticking on gamely into midfield. Draws much kinder this time and deserves far more respect. TORRITA (10) chased well into fourth at Strathalbyn last start. The draw isn't as kind this time, but she remains one to follow up.
